This dataset contains percentage changes in UK house price since 1986 from the Office for National Statistics.

Click the link below to download the dataset for this worksheet to your hard drive.

house_prices.xlsx

Youll need the readxl, dplyr, and ggplot2 packages.

You will have to filter the data before you plot it.
